title: 3rd Floor Coming Soon
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 988 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Grandview Terrace Apartments is a gorgeous community located in the upscale Lake Minnetonka area.', 'Grandview has a park-like setting that is quiet and tranquil.', 'Conveniently located in the city of Mound.', "Just a stone's throw to Harrison Bay on Lake Minnetonka, steps from Downtown Mound, the library and the bus line.", 'Drive just 10 minutes to Ridgedale Mall and 20 minutes to MPLS.', 'Enjoy all that Lake Minnetonka has to offer, walking or biking on one of the many trails, hiking in one of the nearby state parks, fishing, boating and fine dining.', 'Grandview offers the finest in carefree living with amenities such as a fitness center, resident activities, and garages with remote doors, elevators, heated swimming pool, and picnic area with new gas grills, secured entries and storage units.', 'The one and two bedroom homes are luxuriously spacious and offer the latest in appliances, lighting, and upgrades.', 'Features:', 'Cable/ Satellite Available, Disposal, Dishwasher, Storage Space, View, Air Conditioner, Patio/Balcony, Hardwood Floors, Large Closets, Refrigerator', 'Community Amenities:', 'On-Site Maintenance, On-Site Parking, Fitness Center, Garage Parking, Controlled Access/Gated, High Speed Internet Available, Elevator, On-Site Management, Courtyard, Laundry Facilities, Near Public Transit, Swimming Pool', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - allowed, One time Fee $200.00, Rent $25.00, Deposit $200.00', 'Comments: Cats and Dogs allowed.', 'Deposit is $200 and $25 rent per pet.', 'Maximum 2 pets allowed.', 'Restrictions: Breed restrictions apply', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5 times the monthly rent', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'O6vnhlbkRTm7']
